# Backend

## Setup

```bash
cd backend
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e .
cp .env.example .env
```

Fill `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` in `.env`.

## Run

```bash
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000
```

## API

- `GET /health`
- `POST /api/v1/ocr/extract` (multipart form with `file`)

Supported file types: `image/jpeg`, `image/png`, `image/webp`

Response shape:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "model_used": "nvidia/nemotron-nano-12b-v2-vl:free",
  "data": {
    "vendor_name": null,
    "invoice_number": null,
    "invoice_date": null,
    "currency": null,
    "total_amount": null,
    "fuel_type": null,
    "product_name": null,
    "product_output_quantity": null,
    "line_items": []
  }
}
```
